            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2296-Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>spinach</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>, <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> and <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min or until the spinach has wilted</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve the<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 150ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2296-Step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
