            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2296-Step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the spinach has wilted, add the<strong> vegetable stock</strong> to the pan with the <strong>crème fraîche</strong> and stir it all together</p><p>Cook for 1 min further or until the sauce is starting to thicken</p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2296-Step-5-x200.jpg",
